title: Grateful Dead Live at Sam Boyd Silver Bowl, U.N.L.V. on 1993-05-14
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi CR-7A) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.8 MHz) >KORG AudioGate 4 > Samplitude Pro X3 Suite > FLAC/24
description:
Set 1

Cold Rain & Snow, Wang Dang Doodle, Lazy River Road, Queen Jane Approximately, Ramble On Rose, Black Throated Wind, Liberty

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain, Way To Go Home, Corinna, Uncle John's Band-> Drums-> Jam-> I Need A Miracle-> Standing On the Moon-> Sugar Magnolia, E: I Fought The Law

Sting opened

reviews.review_text:
a harvest moon of the few things I remember about this insane show was finding my way to a top bleacher row to try and get some relief from the days wicked heat. The sun was nearly down and the moon was huge, full and orange/reddish. a harvest moon.
suddenly Jerry kicks out a Standing on the Moon.
WOW!!!!
